<template>
  <v-app-bar dark app variant="dark" fixed="top">
    <v-toolbar-title>テシュカン</v-toolbar-title><v-spacer></v-spacer>
    <router-link class="navbar-brand " to="/SubmissionManagement">提出物管理</router-link>
    <router-link class="navbar-brand " to="/MemberManagement">メンバー管理</router-link>
    <v-btn @click="submissionManagement()">
      <svg-icon type="mdi" :path="accountGroup"></svg-icon>提出物管理
    </v-btn>
    <v-btn @click="memberManagement()">
      <svg-icon type="mdi" :path="accountGroup"></svg-icon>メンバー管理
    </v-btn>
    <v-btn @click="groupManagement()">
      <svg-icon type="mdi" :path="accountGroup"></svg-icon>グループ管理
    </v-btn>
    <v-btn @click="logout()">
      <svg-icon type="mdi" :path="applicationExport"></svg-icon>
    </v-btn>
  </v-app-bar>
</template>

<script>
import SvgIcon from '@jamescoyle/vue-icon';
import { mdiApplicationExport } from '@mdi/js';
import { mdiAccountSupervisorCircle } from '@mdi/js';
export default {
  name: "my-component",
  components: {
    SvgIcon
  },
  data() {
    return {
      applicationExport: mdiApplicationExport,
      accountGroup: mdiAccountSupervisorCircle,

    }
  },
  methods: {
    logout() {
      this.$router.push(
        "/"
      );
    },
    groupManagement() {
      this.$router.push(
        "/GroupManagement"
      );
    },
  }
}
</script>

<style scoped>
v-app-bar {
  text-align: center;

  width: 100%;
}
</style>
